s\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:155:\"Keep silence before me, O islands; and let the people renew their strength: let them come near; then let them speak: let us come near together to judgment.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:1;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:2;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:202:\"Who raised up the righteous man from the east, called him to his foot, gave the nations before him, and made him rule over kings? he gave them as the dust to his sword, and as driven stubble to his bow.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:2;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:3;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:87:\"He pursued them, and passed safely; even by the way that he had not gone with his feet.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:3;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:4;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:124:\"Who hath wrought and done it, calling the generations from the beginning? I the LORD, the first, and with the last; I am he.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:4;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:5;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:85:\"The isles saw it, and feared; the ends of the earth were afraid, drew near, and came.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:5;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:6;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:91:\"They helped every one his neighbour; and every one said to his brother, Be of good courage.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:6;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:7;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:204:\"So the carpenter encouraged the goldsmith, and he that smootheth with the hammer him that smote the anvil, saying, It is ready for the sodering: and he fastened it with nails, that it should not be moved.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:7;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:8;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:90:\"But thou, Israel, art my servant, Jacob whom I have chosen, the seed of Abraham my friend.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:8;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:9;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:179:\"Thou whom I have taken from the ends of the earth, and called thee from the chief men thereof, and said unto thee, Thou art my servant; I have chosen thee, and not cast thee away.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:9;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:10;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:184:\"¶ Fear thou not; for I am with thee: be not dismayed; for I am thy God: I will strengthen thee; yea, I will help thee; yea, I will uphold thee with the right hand of my righteousness.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:10;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:11;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:152:\"Behold, all they that were incensed against thee shall be ashamed and confounded: they shall be as nothing; and they that strive with thee shall perish.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:11;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:12;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:156:\"Thou shalt seek them, and shalt not find them, even them that contended with thee: they that war against thee shall be as nothing, and as a thing of nought.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:12;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:13;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:94:\"For I the LORD thy God will hold thy right hand, saying unto thee, Fear not; I will help thee.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:13;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:14;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:124:\"Fear not, thou worm Jacob, and ye men of Israel; I will help thee, saith the LORD, and thy redeemer, the Holy One of Israel.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:14;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:15;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:160:\"Behold, I will make thee a new sharp threshing instrument having teeth: thou shalt thresh the mountains, and beat them small, and shalt make the hills as chaff.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:15;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:16;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:173:\"Thou shalt fan them, and the wind shall carry them away, and the whirlwind shall scatter them: and thou shalt rejoice in the LORD, and shalt glory in the Holy One of Israel.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:16;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:17;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:161:\"When the poor and needy seek water, and there is none, and their tongue faileth for thirst, I the LORD will hear them, I the God of Israel will not forsake them.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:17;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:18;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:156:\"I will open rivers in high places, and fountains in the midst of the valleys: I will make the wilderness a pool of water, and the dry land springs of water.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:18;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:19;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:173:\"I will plant in the wilderness the cedar, the shittah tree, and the myrtle, and the oil tree; I will set in the desert the fir tree, and the pine, and the box tree together:\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:19;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:20;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:153:\"That they may see, and know, and consider, and understand together, that the hand of the LORD hath done this, and the Holy One of Israel hath created it.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:20;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:21;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:93:\"Produce your cause, saith the LORD; bring forth your strong reasons, saith the King of Jacob.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:21;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:22;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:198:\"Let them bring them forth, and shew us what shall happen: let them shew the former things, what they be, that we may consider them, and know the latter end of them; or declare us things for to come.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:22;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:23;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:153:\"Shew the things that are to come hereafter, that we may know that ye are gods: yea, do good, or do evil, that we may be dismayed, and behold it together.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:23;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:24;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:91:\"Behold, ye are of nothing, and your work of nought: an abomination is he that chooseth you.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:24;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:25;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:190:\"I have raised up one from the north, and he shall come: from the rising of the sun shall he call upon my name: and he shall come upon princes as upon morter, and as the potter treadeth clay.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:25;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:26;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:217:\"Who hath declared from the beginning, that we may know? and beforetime, that we may say, He is righteous? yea, there is none that sheweth, yea, there is none that declareth, yea, there is none that heareth your words.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:26;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:27;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:110:\"The first shall say to Zion, Behold, behold them: and I will give to Jerusalem one that bringeth good tidings.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:27;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:28;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:130:\"For I beheld, and there was no man; even among them, and there was no counsellor, that, when I asked of them, could answer a word.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:28;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:29;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:97:\"Behold, they are all vanity; their works are nothing: their molten images are wind and confusion.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}}s:10:\"verseCount\";i:29;s:11:\"translation\";s:3:\"KJV\";s:7:\"bibleId\";s:19:\"de4e12af7f28f599-02\";s:4:\"next\";a:3:{s:2:\"id\";s:6:\"ISA.42\";s:6:\"number\";s:2:\"42\";s:6:\"bookId\";s:3:\"ISA\";}s:8:\"previous\";a:3:{s:2:\"id\";s:6:\"ISA.40\";s:6:\"number\";s:2:\"40\";s:6:\"bookId\";s:3:\"ISA\";}}',1769946596),('laravel-cache-bible.chapter.de4e12af7f28f599-02.PHP.3','a:10:{s:7:\"success\";b:1;s:9:\"reference\";s:13:\"Philippians 3\";s:6:\"bookId\";s:3:\"PHP\";s:7:\"chapter\";i:3;s:6:\"verses\";a:21:{i:0;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:1;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:129:\"Finally, my brethren, rejoice in the Lord. To write the same things to you, to me indeed is not grievous, but for you it is safe.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:1;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:2;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:64:\"Beware of dogs, beware of evil workers, beware of the concision.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:2;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:3;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:127:\"For we are the circumcision, which worship God in the spirit, and rejoice in Christ Jesus, and have no confidence in the flesh.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:3;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:4;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:133:\"Though I might also have confidence in the flesh. If any other man thinketh that he hath whereof he might trust in the flesh, I more:\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:4;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:5;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:136:\"Circumcised the eighth day, of the stock of Israel, of the tribe of Benjamin, an Hebrew of the Hebrews; as touching the law, a Pharisee;\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:5;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:6;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:99:\"Concerning zeal, persecuting the church; touching the righteousness which is in the law, blameless.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:6;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:7;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:65:\"But what things were gain to me, those I counted loss for Christ.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:7;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:8;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:207:\"Yea doubtless, and I count all things but loss for the excellency of the knowledge of Christ Jesus my Lord: for whom I have suffered the loss of all things, and do count them but dung, that I may win Christ,\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:8;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:9;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:167:\"And be found in him, not having mine own righteousness, which is of the law, but that which is through the faith of Christ, the righteousness which is of God by faith:\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:9;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:10;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:132:\"That I may know him, and the power of his resurrection, and the fellowship of his sufferings, being made conformable unto his death;\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:10;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:11;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:65:\"If by any means I might attain unto the resurrection of the dead.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:11;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:12;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:164:\"Not as though I had already attained, either were already perfect: but I follow after, if that I may apprehend that for which also I am apprehended of Christ Jesus.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:12;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:13;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:171:\"Brethren, I count not myself to have apprehended: but this one thing I do, forgetting those things which are behind, and reaching forth unto those things which are before,\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:13;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:14;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:81:\"I press toward the mark for the prize of the high calling of God in Christ Jesus.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:14;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:15;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:137:\"Let us therefore, as many as be perfect, be thus minded: and if in any thing ye be otherwise minded, God shall reveal even this unto you.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:15;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:16;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:105:\"Nevertheless, whereto we have already attained, let us walk by the same rule, let us mind the same thing.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:16;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:17;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:97:\"Brethren, be followers together of me, and mark them which walk so as ye have us for an ensample.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:17;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:18;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:127:\"(For many walk, of whom I have told you often, and now tell you even weeping, that they are the enemies of the cross of Christ:\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:18;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:19;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:112:\"Whose end is destruction, whose God is their belly, and whose glory is in their shame, who mind earthly things.)\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:19;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:20;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:99:\"For our conversation is in heaven; from whence also we look for the Saviour, the Lord Jesus Christ:\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:20;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:21;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:169:\"Who shall change our vile body, that it may be fashioned like unto his glorious body, according to the working whereby he is able even to subdue all things unto himself.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}}s:10:\"verseCount\";i:21;s:11:\"translation\";s:3:\"KJV\";s:7:\"bibleId\";s:19:\"de4e12af7f28f599-02\";s:4:\"next\";a:3:{s:2:\"id\";s:5:\"PHP.4\";s:6:\"number\";s:1:\"4\";s:6:\"bookId\";s:3:\"PHP\";}s:8:\"previous\";a:3:{s:2:\"id\";s:5:\"PHP.2\";s:6:\"number\";s:1:\"2\";s:6:\"bookId\";s:3:\"PHP\";}}',1769465271),('laravel-cache-bible.chapter.de4e12af7f28f599-02.PHP.4','a:10:{s:7:\"success\";b:1;s:9:\"reference\";s:13:\"Philippians 4\";s:6:\"bookId\";s:3:\"PHP\";s:7:\"chapter\";i:4;s:6:\"verses\";a:23:{i:0;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:1;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:117:\"Therefore, my brethren dearly beloved and longed for, my joy and crown, so stand fast in the Lord, my dearly beloved.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:1;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:2;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:83:\"I beseech Euodias, and beseech Syntyche, that they be of the same mind in the Lord.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:2;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:3;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:187:\"And I intreat thee also, true yokefellow, help those women which laboured with me in the gospel, with Clement also, and with other my fellowlabourers, whose names are in the book of life.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:3;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:4;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:52:\"Rejoice in the Lord alway: and again I say, Rejoice.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:4;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:5;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:63:\"Let your moderation be known unto all men. The Lord is at hand.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:5;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:6;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:129:\"Be careful for nothing; but in every thing by prayer and supplication with thanksgiving let your requests be made known unto God.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:6;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:7;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:109:\"And the peace of God, which passeth all understanding, shall keep your hearts and minds through Christ Jesus.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:7;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:8;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:275:\"Finally, brethren, whatsoever things are true, whatsoever things are honest, whatsoever things are just, whatsoever things are pure, whatsoever things are lovely, whatsoever things are of good report; if there be any virtue, and if there be any praise, think on these things.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:8;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:9;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:126:\"Those things, which ye have both learned, and received, and heard, and seen in me, do: and the God of peace shall be with you.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:9;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:10;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:152:\"But I rejoiced in the Lord greatly, that now at the last your care of me hath flourished again; wherein ye were also careful, but ye lacked opportunity.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:10;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:11;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:107:\"Not that I speak in respect of want: for I have learned, in whatsoever state I am, therewith to be content.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:11;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:12;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:170:\"I know both how to be abased, and I know how to abound: every where and in all things I am instructed both to be full and to be hungry, both to abound and to suffer need.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:12;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:13;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:58:\"I can do all things through Christ which strengtheneth me.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:13;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:14;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:78:\"Notwithstanding ye have well done, that ye did communicate with my affliction.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:14;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:15;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:178:\"Now ye Philippians know also, that in the beginning of the gospel, when I departed from Macedonia, no church communicated with me as concerning giving and receiving, but ye only.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:15;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:16;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:66:\"For even in Thessalonica ye sent once and again unto my necessity.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:16;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:17;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:80:\"Not because I desire a gift: but I desire fruit that may abound to your account.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:17;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:18;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:179:\"But I have all, and abound: I am full, having received of Epaphroditus the things which were sent from you, an odour of a sweet smell, a sacrifice acceptable, wellpleasing to God.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:18;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:19;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:87:\"But my God shall supply all your need according to his riches in glory by Christ Jesus.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:19;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:20;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:61:\"Now unto God and our Father be glory for ever and ever. Amen.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:20;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:21;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:77:\"Salute every saint in Christ Jesus. The brethren which are with me greet you.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:21;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:22;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:73:\"All the saints salute you, chiefly they that are of Caesar’s household.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:22;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:23;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:57:\"The grace of our Lord Jesus Christ be with you all. Amen.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}}s:10:\"verseCount\";i:23;s:11:\"translation\";s:3:\"KJV\";s:7:\"bibleId\";s:19:\"de4e12af7f28f599-02\";s:4:\"next\";a:3:{s:2:\"id\";s:9:\"COL.intro\";s:6:\"number\";s:5:\"intro\";s:6:\"bookId\";s:3:\"COL\";}s:8:\"previous\";a:3:{s:2:\"id\";s:5:\"PHP.3\";s:6:\"number\";s:1:\"3\";s:6:\"bookId\";s:3:\"PHP\";}}',1769955851),('laravel-cache-bible.chapter.de4e12af7f28f599-02.PSA.47','a:10:{s:7:\"success\";b:1;s:9:\"reference\";s:9:\"Psalms 47\";s:6:\"bookId\";s:3:\"PSA\";s:7:\"chapter\";i:47;s:6:\"verses\";a:9:{i:0;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:1;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:75:\"O clap your hands, all ye people; shout unto God with the voice of triumph.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:1;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:2;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:74:\"For the LORD most high is terrible; he is a great King over all the earth.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:2;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:3;s:8:\"segments\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:68:\"He shall subdue the people under us, and the nations under our feet.\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"normal\";}}s:15:\"hasWordsOfJesus\";b:0;}i:3;a:3:{s:6:\"number\";i:4;s:8:\"se