INSERT INTO `egw_references` VALUES ('019be9b0-dd8c-73e4-b022-ed1e5d8e0cf7','Ministry of Healing','MH',NULL,238,NULL,NULL,'Many who might be strong and useful have become invalids through indolence. The vigor of the mind and the strength of the body are largely dependent on the amount of exercise taken. Both are strengthened by activity and enfeebled by inaction.','Importance of Exercise','This quote emphasizes that consistent physical activity strengthens both mental faculties and the physical body, including muscles and bones, preventing weakness and disease caused by a sedentary lifestyle.','2026-01-23 00:10:41','2026-01-23 00:10:41',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019be9b1-024b-73bc-8fc2-2b454f36ef75','Ministry of Healing','MH',NULL,238,NULL,NULL,'Many who might be strong and useful have become invalids through indolence. The vigor of the mind and the strength of the body are largely dependent on the amount of exercise taken. Both are strengthened by activity and enfeebled by inaction.','Importance of Exercise','This quote emphasizes that consistent physical activity strengthens both mental faculties and the physical body, including muscles and bones, preventing weakness and disease caused by a sedentary lifestyle.','2026-01-23 00:10:50','2026-01-23 00:28:24','2026-01-23 00:28:24',1,1,1),('019bf0dd-3cdb-721e-9a26-d64123b6d301','Ministry of Healing','MH',NULL,127,128,NULL,'True temperance teaches us to abstain entirely from that which is injurious, and to use judiciously that which is healthful.','Temperance','Emphasis on abstaining from the harmful and using the healthful.','2026-01-24 09:36:29','2026-01-24 09:36:29',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019bf0dd-3cdc-7344-8fff-8ee5520572d0','Counsels on Diet and Foods','CD',NULL,44,45,NULL,'The diet reform should be progressive...It is impossible to make an entire change all at once, but every advance made is a gain.','Diet','Emphasis on a progressive approach to dietary changes.','2026-01-24 09:36:29','2026-01-24 09:36:29',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019bf0dd-3cdd-71ee-80e6-3fc5a97fabcc','Counsels on Health','CH',NULL,115,NULL,NULL,'Pure air, sunlight, abstemiousness, rest, exercise, proper diet, the use of water, trust in divine power--these are the true remedies.','Natural Remedies','The eight natural remedies','2026-01-24 09:36:29','2026-01-24 09:36:29',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019bf0ef-c570-726c-b6f5-9bbba94f09b3','Ministry of Healing','MH',NULL,258,259,NULL,'Pure air, sunlight, abstemiousness, rest, exercise, proper diet, the use of water, trust in divine power—these are the true remedies. Every person has a knowledge of these things; but there are many who do not use them as they should.','Lifestyle Factors in Healing','Highlights the importance of lifestyle factors in healing.','2026-01-24 09:56:44','2026-01-24 09:56:44',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019bf0ef-c574-7252-98fd-a67ca3085c1c','Counsels on Diet and Foods','CD',NULL,92,NULL,NULL,'In order to preserve health, temperance in all things is necessary—temperance in labor, temperance in eating and drinking.','Moderation','Emphasizes the importance of moderation.','2026-01-24 09:56:44','2026-01-24 09:56:44',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019bf0ef-c575-70ed-8fe6-85b598983597','Counsels on Health','CH',NULL,115,NULL,NULL,'Many suffer from pain, not because they need medicine, but because they are neglecting to take care of their bodies.','Self-Care','Highlights the importance of self-care.','2026-01-24 09:56:44','2026-01-24 09:56:44',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019bf3d5-04c5-7057-b0cd-e66a2d559413','Ministry of Healing','MH',NULL,261,NULL,NULL,'Pure air, sunlight, abstemiousness, rest, exercise, proper diet, the use of water, trust in divine power--these are the true remedies.','Natural Remedies','Emphasizes lifestyle factors in promoting healing and well-being.','2026-01-24 23:26:22','2026-01-24 23:26:22',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019bf3d5-04c7-735d-9c35-ec59ef0dcee4','Counsels on Diet and Foods','CD',NULL,388,NULL,NULL,'If you desire health, take it into your own hands, and take the word of God for your medicine.','Diet','Highlights the role of personal responsibility and spiritual faith in health restoration.','2026-01-24 23:26:22','2026-01-24 23:26:22',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019bf3d5-04c8-709f-89c2-9b6ac88d351c','Counsels on Health','CH',NULL,125,NULL,NULL,'Our bodies are Christ\'s purchased possession, and we are not at liberty to treat them as we please. To neglect the laws of our being is to dishonor God.','Health','Underscores the importance of taking care of our bodies as temples of the Holy Spirit.','2026-01-24 23:26:22','2026-01-24 23:26:22',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019bf3d5-04c9-7368-87b8-01aa8befe703','Ministry of Healing','MH',NULL,296,NULL,NULL,'In order to have perfect health, your heart must be joyful, and your mind free from anxiety.','Mental Health','Stresses the importance of mental and emotional well-being in overall health.','2026-01-24 23:26:22','2026-01-24 23:26:22',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019bf501-f732-7038-9230-8e8e178ca40b','Ministry of Healing','MH',NULL,241,NULL,NULL,'Pure air, sunlight, abstemiousness, rest, exercise, proper diet, the use of water, trust in divine power--these are the true remedies. Every person has a knowledge of these remedies; but there are many who do not appreciate them as they should. They are remedies that nature provides, and that can be used by anyone.','General Principle',NULL,'2026-01-25 04:55:05','2026-01-25 04:55:05',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019bf501-f734-717b-88b2-d8d4024d6926','Ministry of Healing','MH',NULL,247,NULL,NULL,'In order to secure health, cheerful spirits, a good conscience, and an assurance of divine favor, let your thoughts be directed to heavenly things.','Focus on Spirituality',NULL,'2026-01-25 04:55:05','2026-01-25 04:55:05',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019bf501-f737-7223-8227-7016197e2f5b','Counsels on Health','CH',NULL,544,NULL,NULL,'The relation that exists between the mind and the body is very intimate. When one is affected, the other sympathizes. The condition of the mind affects the health to a far greater degree than many realize.','Mind-Body Connection',NULL,'2026-01-25 04:55:05','2026-01-25 04:55:05',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019bf501-f73b-735f-a629-d3875ae00059','Counsels on Health','CH',NULL,587,NULL,NULL,'A quiet, cheerful spirit is a great blessing, not only physically but spiritually. It is a treasure more precious than gold.','Importance of a Cheerful Spirit',NULL,'2026-01-25 04:55:05','2026-01-25 04:55:05',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019bf503-6ebe-7034-8402-8e1f73c981be','Counsels on Diet and Foods','CD',NULL,108,NULL,NULL,'Grains, fruits, nuts, and vegetables constitute the diet chosen for us by our Creator. These foods, prepared in as simple and natural a manner as possible, are the most healthful and nourishing. They impart a strength, a power of endurance, and a vigor of intellect that are not afforded by a more complex and stimulating diet.','Diet','This quote emphasizes the benefits of a plant-based diet for overall health.','2026-01-25 04:56:41','2026-01-25 04:56:41',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019bf505-0c52-71dc-ba0a-432d2556b532','Counsels on Diet and Foods','CD',NULL,156,NULL,NULL,'In order to preserve health, temperance in all things is necessary—temperance in labor, temperance in eating and drinking.','Temperance','Emphasizes moderation in all aspects of life for maintaining optimal health.','2026-01-25 04:58:27','2026-01-25 04:58:27',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019bf506-1e06-735d-b2cc-88a25deb5674','Ministry of Healing','MH',NULL,128,NULL,NULL,'Pure air, sunlight, abstemiousness, rest, exercise, proper diet, the use of water, trust in divine power – these are the true remedies.','Natural Remedies','Emphasizes the importance of lifestyle factors in promoting health and well-being, which are crucial for managing IBS.','2026-01-25 04:59:37','2026-01-25 04:59:37',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019bf506-1e0a-7300-a8ee-0249f89cff9f','Counsels on Diet and Foods','CD',NULL,191,NULL,NULL,'The stomach is a sensitive organ, and it is to be treated with respect. It should not be loaded with food that is difficult to digest.','Diet','Highlights the need to be mindful of dietary choices and avoid foods that may trigger IBS symptoms.','2026-01-25 04:59:37','2026-01-25 04:59:37',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019bf506-1e0d-7030-a383-b874f07e6d83','Counsels on Health','CH',NULL,372,NULL,NULL,'Those who suffer from nervous disorders should avoid condiments and stimulating drinks. They should also avoid taking a large amount of salt.','Diet','Suggests avoiding substances that can irritate the digestive system and exacerbate IBS symptoms.','2026-01-25 04:59:37','2026-01-25 04:59:37',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019bf506-1e10-711f-a92d-450326114bb5','Ministry of Healing','MH',NULL,257,NULL,NULL,'The relation that exists between the mind and the body is very intimate. When one is affected, the other sympathizes.','Mental Health','Reinforces the brain-gut axis connection, emphasizing the importance of mental and emotional well-being in managing IBS.','2026-01-25 04:59:37','2026-01-25 04:59:37',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019bf507-bf75-7046-9016-c1b0be585bbb','Counsels on Diet and Foods','CD',NULL,90,NULL,NULL,'Disease never comes without a cause. The way is prepared, and disease invited. Wrong habits of eating and drinking, and neglect of physical exercise, are the great predisposing causes of disease.','Diet','Highlights the role of lifestyle factors, particularly diet and exercise, in the development of disease.','2026-01-25 05:01:24','2026-01-25 05:01:24',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019bf507-bf79-7368-ab7b-27d76f43a243','Counsels on Health','CH',NULL,61,NULL,NULL,'Nature\'s remedies should be used intelligently. We are to co-operate with God in the recovery of health. Exercise, pure air and sunlight, nutritious food, and a cheerful frame of mind are the remedies that God has provided for the restoration of health. These are nature\'s remedies, and when properly used, they will prove a great blessing.','Natural Remedies','Reinforces the importance of natural remedies and a positive mental attitude for health restoration.','2026-01-25 05:01:24','2026-01-25 05:01:24',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019bf507-bf7c-7289-9bdc-ab581d802380','Ministry of Healing','MH',NULL,235,NULL,NULL,'Many are suffering from disease of the mind, far more than from disease of the body. Distress of mind never helps the body. It saps the life forces, and tends to decay and death.','Mental Health','Highlights the profound connection between mental and physical health. Addressing mental distress is vital for overall well-being.','2026-01-25 05:01:24','2026-01-25 05:01:24',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019bf508-f8dc-73d7-9d73-4f38a50fbd21','Counsels on Diet and Foods','CD',NULL,121,NULL,NULL,'Stimulating food is injurious to the digestive organs, and indirectly affects the brain and nerves.','Diet','Emphasizes the connection between diet and brain health.','2026-01-25 05:02:44','2026-01-25 05:02:44',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019bf508-f8de-72ae-8283-ce2d215fb365','Counsels on Health','CH',NULL,71,NULL,NULL,'In order to have sound minds, we must have sound bodies. As our bodies are affected, so are our minds affected.','Health','Highlights the importance of physical health for mental well-being.','2026-01-25 05:02:44','2026-01-25 05:02:44',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019c16ea-8543-726c-827b-1b8ffd1f0637','Counsels on Diet and Foods','CD',NULL,56,NULL,NULL,'A diet too stimulating, indulged in freely, weakens the intellect and arouses the animal passions, giving them the ascendancy over the mental and moral powers.','Diet','Connection between diet and overall health','2026-01-31 18:56:34','2026-01-31 18:56:34',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019c16ea-8545-718b-8328-4748539c0ade','Counsels on Health','CH',NULL,60,NULL,NULL,'We must eat to live, not live to eat.','Diet','Moderation in diet','2026-01-31 18:56:34','2026-01-31 18:56:34',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019c16ea-8548-72a5-9df1-5468d859127a','Ministry of Healing','MH',NULL,295,NULL,NULL,'Let the patient feel that he is not left to fight the battle alone. Encourage him to look to the mighty Healer. Tell him that God loves him, and that His love is the best of remedies.','Spiritual Care','Importance of spiritual support in healing','2026-01-31 18:56:34','2026-01-31 18:56:34',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019c1709-2f10-71ad-8f73-13b7f323ca45','Counsels on Diet and Foods','CD',NULL,69,NULL,NULL,'Pure air, sunlight, abstemiousness, rest, exercise, proper diet, the use of water, trust in divine power--these are the true remedies.','Natural Remedies, Lifestyle Medicine','Highlights the importance of lifestyle factors in promoting health and healing, which aligns with the lifestyle medicine approach to NAFLD management.','2026-01-31 19:30:03','2026-01-31 19:30:03',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019c1709-2f12-72cc-8d1f-32b41fac12fd','Counsels on Diet and Foods','CD',NULL,311,NULL,NULL,'Tea and coffee are stimulants, and as such produce a temporary exhilaration, but the after-effect is exhaustion. These habits create an irritation of the nerves and cause a waste of the life forces; the after-effects of these nerve irritants are always depressing. Stimulants do not impart strength. As the system becomes exhausted, and as strength is apparently needed, there is a resort to stimulants. This is the practice when men and women are overworked.','Stimulants, Coffee','Although current research suggests potential benefits of moderate coffee consumption, this quote highlights the importance of understanding the long-term effects of stimulants and avoiding reliance on them for energy.','2026-01-31 19:30:03','2026-01-31 19:30:03',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019c1709-2f19-7149-8a5a-cb22edf6afe5','Counsels on Health','CH',NULL,37,NULL,NULL,'Overeating is a sin against physical and moral law. The gratification of the appetite is too often at the expense of health.','Diet, Overeating','Underscores the importance of mindful eating and avoiding overconsumption, which is particularly relevant to managing weight and insulin resistance in NAFLD.','2026-01-31 19:30:03','2026-01-31 19:30:03',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019c1709-2f1a-7009-b802-a47d153cd92c','Ministry of Healing','MH',NULL,305,NULL,NULL,'The relation that exists between the mind and the body is very intimate. When one is affected, the other sympathizes. The condition of the mind affects the health to a far greater degree than many realize. Many of the diseases from which men suffer are the result of mental depression. Grief, anxiety, discontent, remorse, guilt, distrust, all tend to break down the life forces and to invite decay and death.','Mind-Body Connection, Mental Health','Emphasizes the mind-body connection and the importance of mental and emotional well-being in promoting physical health.','2026-01-31 19:30:03','2026-01-31 19:30:03',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019c170a-c308-72e2-a368-af22420d5e18','Ministry of Healing','MH',NULL,236,NULL,NULL,'In the treatment of the sick, the effect of mind on body should not be overlooked. When pain is felt, the patient should, as far as possible, be led to turn the thoughts away from self and to fix them upon cheerful, hopeful subjects.','Mind-Body Connection','Directing thoughts away from pain to hopeful subjects for healing.','2026-01-31 19:31:47','2026-01-31 19:31:47',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019c1719-33c2-7269-b6c7-4202839393a9','Counsels on Diet and Foods','CD',NULL,176,NULL,NULL,'The great need of the system is not medicine, but proper food, pure air, proper exercise, and regularity in all things.','Diet and Lifestyle','This quote emphasizes the role of diet and lifestyle in maintaining health and preventing disease, which is particularly relevant for managing PCOS.','2026-01-31 19:47:33','2026-01-31 19:47:33',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019c171c-3fe3-7381-be1a-41c6239f4e70','The Ministry of Healing','MH',NULL,127,NULL,NULL,'Pure air, sunlight, abstemiousness, rest, exercise, proper diet, the use of water, trust in divine power—these are the true remedies.','Natural Remedies',NULL,'2026-01-31 19:50:53','2026-01-31 19:50:53',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019c171c-3fe8-7008-8583-33de2a3895c3','Counsels on Diet and Foods','CD',NULL,37,NULL,NULL,'In order to preserve health, temperance in all things is necessary—temperance in labor, temperance in eating and drinking.','Temperance',NULL,'2026-01-31 19:50:53','2026-01-31 19:50:53',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019c171c-3ff6-70db-8d6e-70f57ed8f4b2','The Ministry of Healing','MH',NULL,241,NULL,NULL,'The relation that exists between the mind and the body is very intimate. When one is affected, the other sympathizes. The condition of the mind affects the health to a far greater degree than many realize. Many of the diseases from which men suffer are the result of mental depression.','Mind-Body Connection',NULL,'2026-01-31 19:50:53','2026-01-31 19:50:53',NULL,1,1,NULL),('019c171c-3ffa-735f-94f5-018950593e21','Counsels on Diet and Foods','CD',NULL,380,NULL,NULL,'The use of flesh-foods is detrimental to health, and vegetables and grains should take the place of flesh in the diet.','Plant-Based Diet',NULL,'2026-01-31 19:50:53','2026-01-31 19:50:53',NULL,1,1,NULL);
