ith PCOS.',NULL,1,1,NULL,'2026-01-31 19:47:33','2026-01-31 19:47:33',NULL),('019c1719-33a8-73bc-b09b-2f52207a4f4c','019c1719-337f-72ff-b711-7a5ab76e8aec','rct','Women with PCOS','A','Multiple RCTs have demonstrated the efficacy of myo-inositol and D-chiro-inositol in improving insulin sensitivity, menstrual regularity, and ovulation in women with PCOS.',NULL,1,1,NULL,'2026-01-31 19:47:33','2026-01-31 19:47:33',NULL),('019c1719-33ad-73d3-8aaa-231b18ab94c5','019bf0dd-3cab-7093-8353-cf4fd5d5c46c','observational','Women with PCOS','B','Studies suggest that mindfulness meditation can reduce stress and improve mood in women with PCOS.',NULL,1,1,NULL,'2026-01-31 19:47:33','2026-01-31 19:47:33',NULL),('019c1719-33b3-709a-8be4-6a749b1cab23','019bf501-f707-7148-9652-4c8846c7c0e2','observational','Women with PCOS','B','Observational studies have linked vitamin D deficiency to increased risk of PCOS and insulin resistance. Some RCTs suggest that vitamin D supplementation may improve metabolic parameters in women with PCOS.',NULL,1,1,NULL,'2026-01-31 19:47:33','2026-01-31 19:47:33',NULL),('019c171c-3fca-710e-aaee-cb7d126bc605','019bf0ef-c516-7072-ad47-036821eb25ab','rct','Adults with migraines','B','A randomized controlled trial published in *Cephalalgia* (2010) found that an elimination diet resulted in a significant reduction in migraine frequency and severity compared to a sham diet.',NULL,1,1,NULL,'2026-01-31 19:50:53','2026-01-31 19:50:53',NULL),('019c171c-3fcd-70f7-96e8-b7de177c8bc5','019bf0ef-c522-7229-9bc3-191fcf5efba5','meta_analysis','Adults with migraines','B','A meta-analysis published in *Headache* (2016) concluded that magnesium supplementation is effective for migraine prevention.','Evidence specifically mentions supplementation, but supports the general principle of magnesium intake.',1,1,NULL,'2026-01-31 19:50:53','2026-01-31 19:50:53',NULL),('019c171c-3fcf-701a-9ac2-9d6d2d0ce8ba','019c171c-3f87-71b5-9aab-be9b7313a11b','rct','Adults with migraines','B','A randomized controlled trial published in *Neurology* (1998) showed that high-dose riboflavin supplementation reduced migraine frequency and severity.','Evidence specifically mentions supplementation, but supports the general principle of riboflavin intake.',1,1,NULL,'2026-01-31 19:50:53','2026-01-31 19:50:53',NULL),('019c171c-3fd1-73e2-a087-6eba2e657f7d','019bf501-f6d8-71a7-9145-c93dabd95c66','systematic_review','Adults with migraines','B','A systematic review published in *The Journal of Headache and Pain* (2011) found that aerobic exercise is an effective non-pharmacological treatment for migraine prevention.',NULL,1,1,NULL,'2026-01-31 19:50:53','2026-01-31 19:50:53',NULL),('019c171c-3fd3-7304-99f6-9ecb1f61df39','019bf0dd-3cab-7093-8353-cf4fd5d5c46c','rct','Adults with migraines','B','A randomized controlled trial published in *Headache* (2014) found that mindfulness-based stress reduction (MBSR) reduced migraine frequency and disability.',NULL,1,1,NULL,'2026-01-31 19:50:53','2026-01-31 19:50:53',NULL),('019c171c-3fd4-72ad-9653-ab7ae64ddfee','019c171c-3f93-7383-82bd-1a2af959e7f6','observational','Adults with migraines','A','Studies have consistently shown a strong correlation between poor sleep hygiene and increased migraine frequency and severity.',NULL,1,1,NULL,'2026-01-31 19:50:53','2026-01-31 19:50:53',NULL),('019c171c-3fd5-735d-838d-8223035742fc','019bf506-1da9-70f1-979a-bd2db8d9d5ae','observational','Migraine sufferers','B','A case-control study in *The Journal of Headache and Pain* showed that migraine sufferers reported lower average daily water intake compared to controls, with inadequate hydration strongly correlated to increased migraine occurrence.',NULL,1,1,NULL,'2026-01-31 19:50:53','2026-01-31 19:50:53',NULL);
